# Documentation Rules for WDIO Starter

## Documentation Structure

1. Organize documentation by topic
2. Use Markdown for documentation
3. Keep documentation up to date
4. Provide examples and code snippets
5. Use clear and concise language

## Documentation Best Practices

1. Document test cases and configuration
2. Add usage examples for page objects
3. Explain project structure and conventions
4. Keep documentation comprehensive
5. Review documentation regularly 